
Ranger Help for: enemy spider
=============================

SUMMARY:
Choosing spider means your Ranger hunts spiders, web-spinners, venomous
arachnids, and similar ambush predators.

This is a strong choice for forests, swamps, deserts, jungles, hills,
mountains, beaches, and underground areas.

COMMAND:
  setenemy spider

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
